<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Password Updated - School Payment</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #f4f6f8;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #2c7be5;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 24px;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px 20px;
        color: #333333;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .footer {
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #999999;
      }
      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          margin: 20px;
        }
        .content {
          padding: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">School Payment Portal</div>
      <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{email}},</p>
        <p>
          Your password for the <strong>School Payment & Dashboard System</strong> has been updated successfully. 
          If you made this change, no further action is required.
        </p>
        <p>
          If you did not update your password, please contact our support team immediately to secure your account.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thanks,<br />
          <strong>School Payment Support Team</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        &copy; {{year}} School Payment Portal. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
